 2. the russian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person playing billiard is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 4. the person playing go is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 8. the malaysian is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
