 7. the dutch is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 8. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 9. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person driving the van and the fan of reggae##7
10. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the pakistani##8
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
12. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
14. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
15. the indian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5

