 4. the social-worker is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is tennis##7
 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
16. the librarian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8

